<br>
Enchanters...  hmm...  i would suggest not using a pet, its only dangerous..  they either mez it or charm it and send it on you..  first off, dispel them.  This will take off their rune and mr.  Then use scars of sigil, they will most likely try to keep you mezed or nuke you or whatnot.  and carry a mod rod.  you will probably need it.  If you have good mr, you will resist mez once and awhile and get that scars in.  a few shots with scars will down the ench.<br>
<br>
